# 🍽️ AI Restaurant Operating System

An AI-powered restaurant management platform that combines:

* 🤖 OpenAI-powered chatbot
* 🍔 Menu-aware ordering system
* 📅 Reservation management
* 🎫 Complaint ticketing
* 📱 WhatsApp notifications
* 🔄 Real-time order tracking with Socket.IO
* 🗄️ MongoDB database

---

# 🚀 Features

## AI Chat Assistant

Customers can interact with an AI assistant to:

* Place food orders
* View available menu items
* Submit complaints
* Contact customer support

---

## Menu Management

Menus are stored in MongoDB and can be dynamically queried by the AI.

Example:

Customer:

> Show me today's menu

Bot:

> 🍔 Burger - ₦2500
> 🍕 Pizza - ₦4000
> 🥤 Coke - ₦500

---

## Order Management

The AI extracts structured order information and creates orders automatically.

Example:

Customer:

> I want 2 burgers and 1 coke

AI Extracts:

```json
{
  "intent": "ORDER",
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Burger",
      "qty": 2
    },
    {
      "name": "Coke",
      "qty": 1
    }
  ]
}
```

---


## Complaint Management

Customers can create complaint tickets.

Example:

> My food arrived cold

Complaint is stored in MongoDB for review.

---

## WhatsApp Restaurant Notifications

Whenever an order is created:

1. Order is saved in MongoDB
2. WhatsApp notification is sent to restaurant staff
3. Staff receives order details instantly

Example:

```
🚨 NEW ORDER

Order ID: 12345

Items:
2x Burger
1x Coke

Total: ₦5500
```

---

## Real-Time Order Tracking

Socket.IO is used to provide live order status updates.

Order lifecycle:

```
pending
↓
confirmed
↓
preparing
↓
ready
↓
delivered
```

Customer receives updates instantly without refreshing the page.

Example:

```
✅ Your order has been confirmed
🍳 Your food is being prepared
🚗 Your order is ready
🎉 Your order has been delivered
```

