# 🧠 AI Intent System

The AI classifies user messages into intents.

Supported intents:

| Intent      | Description             |
| ----------- | ----------------------- |
| ORDER       | Create food order       |
| MENU_QUERY  | Fetch available menu    |          |
| COMPLAINT   | Create complaint ticket |
| SUPPORT     | Customer support        |
| GENERAL     | General conversation    |

