# 🔌 Socket.IO

Backend emits:

```js
io.emit("orderUpdated", {
  orderId,
  status,
});
```

Frontend listens:

```js
socket.on("orderUpdated", (data) => {
  console.log(data);
});
```

---

# 📱 WhatsApp Integration

The system uses Meta WhatsApp Cloud API.

Workflow:

```
Order Created
      ↓
WhatsApp Notification
      ↓
Restaurant Staff
      ↓
Webhook Receives Reply
      ↓
Order Status Updated
      ↓
Socket.IO Event
      ↓
Customer Notification
```

